summary: Spiderman/Peter Parker was always a character I felt peripheral fondness of, but nothing more. Like, you go you funky little...
body: Spiderman/Peter Parker was always a character I felt peripheral fondness of, but nothing more. Like, you go you funky little webslinger, good for you, but otherwise… ehh?. Until someone introduced me to the very EXCELLENT thought of him being a trans guy and then suddenly my brain was like !!!!!!!!! this is CORRECT, we must adopt him into our heart and home IMMEDIATELY cuz that’s the rep I want for myself. It just… makes so much sense, feels so right, and what I’m saying is accept trans guy peter parker into your heart because its the highest, most god tier version of him you could accept.

body:
PSA:

Hey idk who tf pays attention to my shitpost of a blog but like y’all idk if I’m gonna be sticking around.

I do cosplay over on Instagram @thespidermatt and Facebook @ The Spider-Matt Cosplay. I’m way more active over there and I’d really appreciate it if you checked it out and gave me a follow. Cosplay is something I’ve gotten super passionate about and my insta has kinda blown up in the past year. I post there at least once a day!!!

Enjoy some pics from this year’s Youmacon of me in my The Amazing Spider-Man 1 preproduction suit. Had a blast shooting in this one.

(Btw I’m probably gonna reblog the shit out of this post so apologies in advance)
